<p><img alt="Perkins Hall" height="116" src="Images/Admin_Offices/Housing/Graphics/OnCampus Headers/WomensHeaders-19.png" style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" width="401" /></p>
<hr />
<p>In Perkins Hall each apartment has a kitchen, living room, and one bathroom.  There are also closets in the hallway for storage.  In the bedrooms, the beds are lofted with a personal desk below.</p>
<hr />
<table border="0" cellpadding="10" style="width: 100%;">
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>
<h2 style="text-align: left;">Amenities:</h2>
<ul>
<li>Extra long twin-size beds in Kerr, Perkins,  Barnes, and Ricks Halls.  Lofted or bunked beds are 61" off the ground and bed rails are  available upon request.</li>
<li>Mattress cover for each bed.</li>
<li>Four square feet of closet space per person.</li>
<li>One three-drawer dresser per person.</li>
<li>One desk and chair per person.</li>
<li>Shelves in each bedroom.</li>
<li>Marker board in living room.</li>
<li>Ironing board and cover.</li>
<li>Kitchen table and four chairs.</li>
<li>Microwave, refrigerator, stove, dishwasher, and pantry in the kitchen.</li>
<li>Two sofas in the living room.</li>
<li>Vacuum, broom, dustpan, mirror, shower curtain, and toliet plunger.</li>
<li>Coin-op laundry facilities.</li>
<li>High-speed wireless internet.</li>
<li>Satellite TV/DVD in main and upper lounges.  Piano in upper lounge.</li>
</ul>
